{"tid":1894930,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【口罩難求】「印尼口罩」包裝盒內數十條蟲蠕動","createTime":"2020-02-24T08:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T14:27:48.000Z","uid":226548,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f7ad89141b5d01fa42d7c8748cef4236890fd57e","tid":1894930,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2555000/2555772/badmask_thumb_20200204_ch_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2555000%2F2555772%2Fbadmask_thumb_20200204_ch_600.jpg&h=432d73b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情持續，本港口罩一罩難求，市面甚至有不少「黑心口罩」湧現。有網民日前發現一盒口罩後，竟然發現<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">盒內布滿如螞蟻般的小蟲，觸目驚心。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有網民今日在facebook群組「將軍澳街坊抗疫自救」發布一段片段，片中事主打開一盒口罩，並把口罩全部從盒中拿出時，盒內底部竟布滿大量如螞蟻般的小蟲不停走動，而盒內的口罩本身亦無獨立包裝，片中事主亦驚呼「勁恐怖」！<br />\n<br />\n至於在「將軍澳街坊抗疫自救」轉載片段的網民則表示，片段是從「mama gp」傳出，片段中的口罩疑似是來自印尼的一款口罩。從網傳段片段可見，片中口罩與印尼「Golden Gloves」口罩款式類近。<br />\n<br />\n隨着本港口罩需求劇增，不少「黑心口罩」亦陸續在市面出現。當中，日本城昨日（2月3日）出售的「Neo 50片裝防護口罩」口罩，事後就有不少成功購買口罩的市民於網上投訴，指購得的口罩質量差，而且沒有防護認證及口罩規格，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">值得留意的是這批口罩的產地同樣來自印尼</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"716d5e15336d0acfabb3f647b4d38d5ed0fde8c1","tid":1894930,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2555772/【口罩難求】口罩荒市面湧現黑心口罩%E3%80%80印尼口罩包裝盒內數十條蟲蠕動\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2555772%2F%E3%80%90%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%9B%A3%E6%B1%82%E3%80%91%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E8%8D%92%E5%B8%82%E9%9D%A2%E6%B9%A7%E7%8F%BE%E9%BB%91%E5%BF%83%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%25E3%2580%2580%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%9D%E7%9B%92%E5%85%A7%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E6%A2%9D%E8%9F%B2%E8%A0%95%E5%8B%95&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAo26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=0d8aed39\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2555772/【口罩難求】口罩荒市面湧現黑心口罩%E3%80%80印尼口罩包裝盒內數十條蟲蠕動</a>"},{"pid":"dfb5bdde65d212c71883b851f5dd72673d83e322","tid":1894930,"uid":256019,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:02:51.000Z","msg":"三星期前舊聞，樓主訓左幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47d20a94b45941a67466becb0bfb0ee9193529e","tid":1894930,"uid":148953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"買左盒都係咁"},{"pid":"10419885fa6e4d85d0eee196e9979d183560a442","tid":1894930,"uid":63697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b47d20a94b45941a67466becb0bfb0ee9193529e","tid":1894930,"uid":148953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"買左盒都係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f1375a7df90b684395a7e873ab33a7d03a3683","tid":1894930,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:44:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34367d4d6d70c4277b48e2a8c428b192a845f359","tid":1894930,"uid":148953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"10419885fa6e4d85d0eee196e9979d183560a442","tid":1894930,"uid":63697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b47d20a94b45941a67466becb0bfb0ee9193529e","tid":1894930,"uid":148953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"買左盒都係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:27:48.000Z","msg":"仲要炒價入左兩盒 好心痛"}]}